本 LoRA 训练界面分为两种模式。: This LoRA Training interface is divided into two modes.
针对新手的简易训练只有部分可调节参数: For beginners, there are only a few adjustable parameters for simple training.
针对有一定经验的用户的专家模式，开放全部的高级参数: For users with some experience, the Expert mode provides access to all advanced parameters.
如果你是新手，建议使用新手模式，不要逞强使用专家模式，否则可能会出现意想不到的问: If you're a beginner, it's recommended to use the Beginner mode. Avoid forcefully using Expert mode, as unexpected issues may arise.
